Update the counters dictionary with the attr min/max restrictions.

This method builds a nested counters mapping per path.

Example:
    {
        "min": [0, 1, 2]
        "max": [3, 4, 5],
        ("c", 1, 0, 1): {
            "min": [6, 7, 8],
            "max": [9, 10, 11],
            ("g", 2, 0, 1): { ... }
        }
    }

Args:
    attr: The source attr instance
    counters: The nested counters instance to update
